import{_ as e,o as t,c as o,b as r}from"./app-a6eacc5a.js";const s={},n=r('<h1 id="pillow-fighting" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#pillow-fighting" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Pillow fighting</h1><p>Pillow fighting is moving <em>out of</em> the bedroom and into the <em>boxing <code>ring</code></em>. The Pillow Fight <code>Championship</code>, or PFC, plans to hold its first live, <em>pay-to-watch</em> event in Florida on January 29.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 枕头大战正在走出卧室，走进拳击场。枕头大战锦标赛计划于1月29日在佛罗里达州举办第一届付费观看的现场直播赛事。</p><p><strong>phrase:</strong><br> out of -&gt; 来自；离开<br> boxing ring -&gt; 拳击场<br> pay-to-watch -&gt; 付费观看</p><p><strong>word:</strong><br> ring<br><code>英: [rɪŋ] 美: [rɪŋ]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 戒指；指环；环状物；圈形的东西<br> v. 包围；环绕；给…戴上金属环（以便将来辨认）；绕…画圆</p></blockquote><p>championship [ 复数 championships ]<br><code>英 [ˈtʃæmpiənʃɪp]美 [ˈtʃæmpiənʃɪp]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 锦标赛；冠军称号，冠军地位；捍卫，拥护</p></blockquote></details><p>Steve Williams had the idea of <em>turning</em> a children&#39;s game <em>into</em> a professional fighting sport. The head of PFC said professional pillow fighting will have the <code>excitement</code> of <em>hand-to-hand</em> fighting without the violence of <em>mixed <code>martial</code> arts</em>, or MMA, and boxing. He said it is not a joke.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 史蒂夫·威廉姆斯产生了这种将儿童游戏变成职业格斗运动的想法。这位枕头大战锦标赛的负责人表示，专业的枕头大战具有肉搏的刺激，却又没有综合格斗和拳击的暴力。他说这可不是个玩笑。</p><p><strong>phrase:</strong><br> turn (sb/sth) into sb/sth -&gt; （使）变成;（使）成为<br> mixed martial arts -&gt; 综合格斗；综合格斗技；综合武术<br> hand-to-hand -&gt; adj. 交手的；白刃的；肉搏的</p><p><strong>word:</strong><br> excitement [ 复数 excitements ]<br><code>英 [ɪkˈsaɪtmənt]美 [ɪkˈsaɪtmənt]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 令人激动（或兴奋）的事，刺激因素；激动，兴奋；性兴奋</p></blockquote><p>martial<br><code>英 [ˈmɑːʃ(ə)l]美 [ˈmɑːrʃ(ə)l]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. &lt;正式&gt;军事的，战争的</p></blockquote></details><p>&quot;It&#39;s not something where you sit there and laugh and <code>feathers</code> are flying,&quot; Williams told <code>Reuters</code>. &quot;It&#39;s serious. It&#39;s <code>hardcore</code> swinging with specialized pillows.&quot;</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 威廉姆斯对路透社表示：“这可不是让你坐在那看羽毛满天飞、然后捧腹大笑的玩闹。这是正儿八经的比赛。它的核心是挥动特制枕头对打。”</p><p><strong>word:</strong><br> feather [feathers feathering feathered ]<br> 英 [ˈfeðə(r)]美 [ˈfeðər]</p><blockquote><p>n. 羽毛；翎毛<br> v. 长羽毛；用羽毛覆盖；在…上装箭羽；使(桨)与水面平行</p></blockquote><p>Reuters<br><code>英 [ˈrɔɪtəz]美 [ˈrɔɪtərz]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 路透社（英国）</p></blockquote><p>hardcore<br><code>英 [ˈhɑːdkɔː(r)]美 [ˈhɑrdˌkɔr; ˈhɑrdˌkor]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 硬核的；赤裸裸描写性行为的<br> n. 硬核；硬底层；碎砖垫层；硬核摇滚乐</p></blockquote></details><p>The three-round fights will be available to view on sports <code>streaming</code> <code>station</code> FITE.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 这些三回合的比赛将可以在体育流媒体网站FITE上观看。</p><p><strong>word:</strong><br> stream [ streams streaming streamed ]<br><code>英: [striːm] 美: [strim]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 流；溪；小河；（液）流<br> v. 流；流动；流出；飘扬<br> 网络 溪流；小溪；数据流</p></blockquote><p>station<br><code>英: [&#39;steɪʃ(ə)n] 美: [ˈsteɪʃ(ə)n]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 站；火车站；电台；电视台<br> v. 派驻；使驻扎；到某处站（或坐）；把…安置到（某处）</p></blockquote></details><p>The male and female <code>athletes</code> in January&#39;s event come mostly from MMA and boxing. But Williams said the athletes are not going to get injured.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 参加一月份比赛的这些男女运动员主要来自于综合格斗和拳击行业。但是威廉姆斯表示，这些运动员不会受伤。</p><p><strong>word:</strong><br> athlete [ 复数 athletes ]<br><code>英 [ˈæθliːt]美 [ˈæθliːt]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 运动员，体育健将；擅长运动的人</p></blockquote></details><p>&quot;The fighters don&#39;t like to get hurt, and there&#39;s a lot of people who don&#39;t want to see the blood. They want to see good competition, they just don&#39;t want to see the violence.&quot;</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> “运动员不想受伤，很多观众也不希望看到流血场面，他们希望看到精彩的比赛，不希望看到暴力。”</p></details><p>Since many people grew up pillow fighting with friends or <code>relatives</code>, Williams hopes the new sport will be <code>relatable</code> and can grow a large audience, including children.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 由于很多人是在跟亲朋好友的枕头大战中长大的，因此威廉姆斯希望这项新运动能够引起人们的共鸣，并吸引包括儿童在内的大量观众。</p><p><strong>word:</strong><br> relative<br><code>英: [&#39;relətɪv] 美: [ˈrelətɪv]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 亲属；亲戚；同类事物<br> adj. 相比较而言的；比较的；相对的；相关联的<br> 网络 相对定位；相关的；亲人</p></blockquote><p>relatable<br><code>UK: /rɪˈleɪ.tə.bəl/ US: /rɪˈleɪ.t̬ə.bəl/</code></p><blockquote><p>v. 使人觉得自己能理解某人<br> adj. 有关系的；可关联的<br> 网络 关联性；体贴的；有关联; 有共鸣</p></blockquote></details><p>&quot;You can call it an <code>alternative</code> sport, but we think <em>it&#39;s going to</em> have <code>mainstream</code> <code>appeal</code>,&quot; he said.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 他说：“你可以称它为一项另类运动，但是我们认为它将会具有主流吸引力。”</p><p><strong>phrase:</strong><br> be going to -&gt; 将要；一般将来时；打算</p><p><strong>word:</strong><br> alternative [ 复数 alternatives ]<br><code>英 [ɔːlˈtɜːnətɪv]美 [ɔːlˈtɜːrnətɪv]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 可供选择的事物，替代物<br> adj. 可替代的，备选的；非传统的，另类的；（两者）互不相容的，非此即彼的</p></blockquote><p>mainstream<br><code>英 [ˈmeɪnstriːm]美 [ˈmeɪnstriːm]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 主流<br> adj. 主流的；（学校，班级）为无特殊需求学生开设的，普通的<br> v. 使主流化，使成为主流；（把有特殊教育需求的孩子）编入普通班级</p></blockquote><p>appeal<br><code>英: [əˈpiːl] 美: [əˈpil]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 上诉；吸引力；申诉；魅力<br> v. 上诉；呼吁；申诉；恳求<br> 网络 有吸引力；请求</p></blockquote></details><p>&quot;Think about how they mixed country music with rap music and <em>brought</em> these <code>diverse</code> audiences <em>together</em>. That&#39;s what we&#39;re doing, and we hope it brings in a different kind of viewer.&quot;</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> “想想人们如何将乡村音乐和说唱音乐融合到一起，并将这些完全不同的观众聚到一起。这就是我们正在做的事情，我们希望它能带来不一样的观众。”</p><p><strong>phrase:</strong><br> bring together -&gt; 使团结；使联合；使聚集</p><p><strong>word:</strong><br> diverse<br><code>英 [daɪˈvɜːs]美 [daɪˈvɜːrs]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 不同的，各式各样的</p></blockquote></details>',19),a=[n];function i(l,c){return t(),o("div",null,a)}const p=e(s,[["render",i],["__file","24-pillow-fighting.html.vue"]]);export{p as default};
